# .graphignore — notes excluded from the knowledge graph (gitignore-style).
# Patterns match note paths relative to the vault root. Blank lines and '#' comments
# are ignored. A trailing "/" matches a directory (and everything under it); "**/" means
# "in any directory". Bare names match by filename anywhere in the vault.

# ── Dependency / build junk accidentally ingested ─────────────────────────────
**/node_modules/

# ── The extracted graph project itself (files moved out to pkm-graph/) ────────
wiki/projects/pkm-evolution/graph/

# ── Generated discovery reports (deliverables, not graph nodes) ───────────────
**/Graph Discovery Report*.md

# ── Generated artifacts & raw captures ────────────────────────────────────────
wiki/artifacts/
wiki/artifact/
**/raw/

# ── Maintenance / pipeline notes ──────────────────────────────────────────────
ingest-queue.md
**/Ingest Queue.md
